<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Stories on My Portfolio</title><link>https://shuvo-paul.github.io/stories/</link><description>Recent content in Stories on My Portfolio</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-US</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 17 Jul 2023 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://shuvo-paul.github.io/stories/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>SICP(JS) Excercise 1.10 explanation</title><link>https://shuvo-paul.github.io/stories/sicp-excercise-110/</link><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jul 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shuvo-paul.github.io/stories/sicp-excercise-110/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The following procedure computes a mathematical function called Ackermann&amp;rsquo;s function.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;function A(x, y) {
 return y === 0
 ? 0
 : x === 0
 ? 2 * y
 : y === 1
 ? 2
 : A(x - 1, A(x, y - 1));
}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;What are the values of the following expressions?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;A (1, 10)
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;A(2, 4)
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;A(3, 3)
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Consider the following procedures, where A is the procedure defined above:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;function f(n) {
 return A(0, n);
}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;function g(n) {
 return A(1, n);
}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;function h(n) {
 return A(2, n);
}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Solutions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Usefull Services that I Like</title><link>https://shuvo-paul.github.io/stories/usefull-services-for-developers/</link><pubDate>Tue, 28 Feb 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shuvo-paul.github.io/stories/usefull-services-for-developers/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="postgress-db"&gt;Postgress DB&lt;/h2&gt;
